data.description: Who doesn't love a Cul-de-sac? Delwood Point at The Preserve is a great little community with two main streets. The pristine home at 4604 Delwood Park Blvd offers you the opportunity for an affordable 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with a gas fireplace, a screened in porch and a yard that backs up to conservation.  This home has plenty of cabinets in the kitchen and in the laundry room. The Master Bedroom feels huge with an extra nook for a desk or for a Reading area,  The split plan is perfect for privacy and the size of the home is easy to maintain without too much stress.  The chance of adding a pool is really good because it has been discussed. The School District is great for resale. The only thing missing here is YOU!
